HEADWORD: Dissimilarly
<hw>Dis*sim"i*lar*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a
dissimilar manner; in a varied style.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With verdant shrubs <qex>dissimilarly</qex> gay.</q> <rj><qau>C.
